archimate:BusinessObject.name: X - Søknadstype/ prosedyre
archimate:BusinessObject.documentation: Tegnene forteller om det er søknad om ny MT (og i så fall type prosedyre), endring, fornyelse osv “MR” for applications for marketing authorisation via MRP “DC” for applications for marketing authorisation via DCP “IA” for Type IA Notifications “IB” for Type IB Notifications “II” for Type II Variations “R” for Renewals “E” for Repeat-use Procedures  “O” for data bases when information in this section is not relevant
